item.title: CVE-2023-6341|2023-11-30T20:50:27.195Z -- catalis -- cms360
item.description: Catalis (previously Icon Software) CMS360 allows a remote, unauthenticated attacker to view sensitive court documents by modifying document and other identifiers in URLs. The impact varies based on the intention and configuration of a specific CMS360 installation.
